198
00:29:30,901 --> 00:29:33,402
Osvetiću se,

199
00:29:33,802 --> 00:29:35,403
Ito Ogami.

200
00:29:36,903 --> 00:29:40,405
I slava će se vratiti imenu Jagjua.

201
00:29:40,905 --> 00:29:46,908
Ako te sada ubijem biće gotovo.

202
00:29:47,408 --> 00:29:49,809
Možeš li me pobediti?

203
00:31:06,740 --> 00:31:07,940
Ubi me!

204
00:31:11,141 --> 00:31:15,443
